Package: sabinaHSBM
Title: Network Reconstruction with Hierarchical Stochastic Block Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Herlander", "Lima",
    email = "limaherlander@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jennifer", "Morales-Barbero",
    role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Provides tools for network reconstruction and link prediction using hierarchical stochastic block models. The package offers an R workflow for preparing binary ecological networks, running model-based reconstruction through the 'graph-tool' Python library, performing cross-validation, evaluating predictive performance, and generating reconstructed interaction matrices.
